                "invention-title": [
                    "Viscosity-reducing surface modifier ZVBA for high-viscosity crude oil, method and application",
                    "一种高粘原油降粘表面改性剂ZVBA、方法及应用"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention belongs to the technical field of materials, and discloses a high-viscosity crude oil viscosity reduction surface modifier ZVBA, a method and application, the chemical composition of the ZVBA is CaHbXd, C is a carbon atom, and a is the number of carbon atoms; h is a hydrogen atom, and b is the number of hydrogen atoms; x is a heteroatom, and d is the number of heteroatoms; the molecular weight of the surface modifier is at least 200, even more than 320, but not more than 10,000 at most. Through use of the surface modifier ZVBA, selectivity and high-viscosity crude oil water phase group surface modification are realized, AOSI between a water group and an oil group is weakened, crude oil viscosity is greatly reduced, fluidity is improved, and the purpose of reducing crude oil system viscosity is realized. And exploitation, transportation and storage of low-strength, low-cost and high-viscosity crude oil without high-temperature steam injection are realized. The method is suitable for exploitation of land thickened oil and exploitation of offshore thickened oil."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明属于材料技术领域，公开了一种高粘原油降粘表面改性剂ZVBA、方法及应用，所述ZVBA的化学组成为：CaHbXd,其中C为碳原子，a为碳原子数目；H为氢原子，b为氢原子数目；X为杂原子，d为杂原子的数目；所述表面改性剂的分子量至少为200，甚至超过320，但最高不会超过10,000。本发明通过表面改性剂ZVBA的使用实现选择性与高粘原油水相团表面改性达到减弱水团与油团间的相互作用AOSI减弱，使得原油粘度大幅度降低、流动性改善，实现原油体系粘度降低的目的，实现无需进行高温蒸汽注入的低强度、低成本高粘原油的开采、运输和储存。该发明既适用于陆地稠油的开采又适用于海上稠油的开采。"
                }
            ]
